.SH Name
.SP 5 5
player_refreshed -  This function gets called by the player object whenever a player refreshes.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void player_refreshed(object player)
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/refresh.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function gets called by the player object whenever
a player refreshes.  You should never call this function directly.

.EP

